#31784
The Frjosa Hel-vegr Tundra~
   A vast and unforgiving tundra.  Looking in any direction proves to be
pointless, as it is all white.  Visibility is three to five feet at best.  
The ground is frozen solid, the air painfully dry and cold, and the wind feels
like daggers.  This is no place for any sane being.  
~
