#31798
Skathe's Retreat~
   A very large dome shaped room, brightly lit by lanterns and a large fire in
the center.  The walls are lined with various furs and hides imported from all
over the world.  The floors are lined with thick carpets and rough hides.  
There is piping leading from the large furnace, in the middle of the room,
going out of the roof.  The room has a calm and warm feeling.  A large variety
of cots are available to rest your head.  
~
